<Placemark><name>Navajo Nation Reservation</name><description><![CDATA[<h3>Navajo Nation Reservation</h3><p><b>&#9888; Tribal overflight assertion (see details).</b> Not FAA-enforced. See navdata PDF.</p><p><b>Nearest airports:</b> <b>E91</b> 17 NM &middot; <b>50AZ</b> 34 NM &middot; <b>K0V7</b> 35 NM</p><p><b>Type:</b> Tribal Designated Statistical Area &nbsp; <b>States:</b> AZ, NM, UT &nbsp; <b>Area:</b> 22,532 sq mi &nbsp; <b>Pop:</b> 166,545</p><p><i>Tap the Points layer for tribal government, website, and more detail. See navdata for overflight considerations.</i></p>]]></description><drawOrder>1</drawOrder><Style><LineStyle><color>ff0020ff</color><width>3.5</width></LineStyle><PolyStyle><color>552060e0</color><fill>1</fill><outline>1</outline></PolyStyle></Style><MultiGeometry><Polygon><tessellate>1</tessellate><outerBoundaryIs><LinearRing><coordinates>-111.89221,36.37121,0 -111.88995,36.37585,0 -111.88740,36.37731,0 -111.87647,36.38095,0 -111.85216,36.38549,0 -111.84781,36.38894,0 -111.84894,36.39386,0 -111.85238,36.39609,0 -111.85852,36.39657,0 -111.87489,36.39186,0 -111.88111,36.39401,0 -111.88353,36.39981,0 -111.86864,36.41228,0 -111.86863,36.41594,0 -111.87239,36.42528,0 -111.87024,36.43100,0 -111.86291,36.43418,0 -111.85256,36.43497,0 -111.84914,36.44581,0 -111.83920,36.44960,0 -111.83569,36.45438,0 -111.83945,36.46703,0 -111.84752,36.47926,0 -111.84741,36.48199,0 -111.84051,36.49239,0 -111.84460,36.49611,0 -111.85684,36.49782,0 -111.85878,36.49953,0 -111.85679,36.50397,0 -111.84991,36.51080,0 -111.84599,36.52100,0 -111.83462,36.53095,0 -111.82803,36.53467,0 -111.82514,36.54915,0 -111.81751,36.55737,0 -111.81061,36.56837,0 -111.80504,36.57305,0 -111.79039,36.57847,0 -111.77223,36.59323,0 -111.76619,36.60079,0 -111.76391,36.60811,0 -111.75863,36.61313,0 -111.75761,36.61653,0 -111.76408,36.62702,0 -111.76092,36.63559,0 -111.76185,36.64344,0 -111.76077,36.64809,0 -111.74515,36.65556,0 -111.74339,36.65788,0 -111.74100,36.66453,0 -111.73935,36.68088,0 -111.73